components.name: ButtonComponent

styleUrlsData.data:
@import ../../assets/styles/sass/colors
@import ../../assets/styles/sass/sizes
@import ../../assets/styles/sass/mixins

button
    padding: 0.469rem 1rem // 7.5px  16px 
    border-radius: 4px
    font-size: $xs // 12px
    font-weight: 700
    outline: none
    cursor: pointer
    color: $black
    background-color: transparent
    border: none
    position: relative
    @include fontStyle()

    &:hover
       background-color: $accentBlue
       transition: 0.3s
       color: $mainBlue

    &:disabled
        cursor: not-allowed

    &:active
        background-color: $darkBlue
        color: $white

.contained
    background: $mainBlue
    color: $white
    border: 0.125rem solid $mainBlue // 2px

    &:disabled
        background: $lightGray
        color: $white
        border: 0.125rem solid $lightGray // 2px

.text
    background-color: transparent
    color: $mainBlue
    border: 0.125rem solid transparent // 2px

    &:hover
       background-color: transparent
       color: $mainBlue

    &:disabled
        color: $lightGray

.outlined
    background-color: transparent
    color: $mainBlue
    border: 0.125rem solid $mainBlue // 2px

    &:disabled
        color: $lightGray
        border: 0.125rem solid $lightGray // 2px

.fullWidth
    width: 100%

.hideContainer
    visibility: hidden
    opacity: 0

.size-small
    font-size: $xs // 12px
    
.size-medium
    font-size: $small // 14px

.loading-container
    position: absolute
    left: calc(50% - 7.5px)
    top: calc(50% - 7.5px)
    width: 100%
    height: 100%

components.name: CardComponent

styleUrlsData.data:
.cs-card
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif
    padding: 10px
    border-radius: 5px
    border-width: thin
    display: block
    max-width: 100%
    outline: none
    text-decoration: none
    transition-property: box-shadow, opacity
    overflow-wrap: break-word
    position: relative
    white-space: normal
    background-color: #FFFFFF

    &-shadow
        box-shadow: 0 2px 1px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, .2), 0 1px 1px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, .14), 0 1px 3px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, .12) !important

components.name: CircularProgressComponent

styleUrlsData.data:
@import ../../assets/styles/sass/colors

.loader
  border: 2px solid $white
  border-radius: 50%
  border-top: 2px solid $mediumGray
  width: 30px
  height: 30px
  -webkit-animation: spin 0.8s linear infinite
  /* Safari
  animation: spin 0.8s linear infinite

/* Safari
@-webkit-keyframes spin
  0%
    -webkit-transform: rotate(0deg)
  100%
    -webkit-transform: rotate(360deg)

@keyframes spin
  0%
    transform: rotate(0deg)
  100%
    transform: rotate(360deg)

styleUrlsData.data:
@import "../../assets/styles/sass/colors"
@import '~material-design-icons/iconfont/material-icons.css'


.cs-input-container
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif
    display: flex
    text-align: center
    align-items: center
    position: relative

i
    position: absolute
    z-index: 2
    display: block
    margin-right: 16px
    text-align: center
    color: $mediumGray
    cursor: pointer
    right: 0

input
    width: 100%
    padding: 8px
    box-sizing: border-box
    outline: none
    color: $black
    border: 1px solid $mediumGray
    border-radius: 4px
    font-size: 12px

    &:focus
        border: 1px solid $mainBlue

    &:focus + .fa
        color: $mainBlue

    &::placeholder
        color: $mediumGray

components.name: SwitchComponent

styleUrlsData.data:
@import "../../assets/styles/sass/colors"

.cs-switch
    position: relative
    display: inline-block
    width: 64px
    height: 32px

    & input
        opacity: 0
        width: 0
        height: 0

.cs-slider
    position: absolute
    cursor: pointer
    top: 0
    left: 0
    right: 0
    bottom: 0
    border: 1px solid $mediumGray
    background-color: $white
    -webkit-transition: .4s
    transition: .4s


    &:before
        position: absolute
        content: ""
        height: 24px
        width: 24px
        left: 4px
        bottom: 3px
        background-color: $mediumGray
        -webkit-transition: .4s
        transition: .4s


    input:checked + &
        background-color: $mainBlue
        border: 1px solid $mainBlue


    input:checked + &:before
        -webkit-transform: translateX(26px)
        -ms-transform: translateX(26px)
        transform: translateX(26px)
        background-color: $white
        left: 8px

    &.cs-round
        border-radius: 34px


    &.cs-round:before
        border-radius: 50%

components.name: TablesComponent

styleUrlsData.data:
@import "../../assets/styles/sass/colors"

.cs-table-roll
  display: inline-block
  width: 100%
  height: calc(100% - 30px)
  margin-top: 2px

table
  font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif
  width: 100%
  table-layout: fixed
  border-collapse: collapse

  thead tr
    height: 30px

    th
      text-align: left
      font-size: 12px
      color: $darkestGray

  tbody
    tr
      height: 40px
      border-bottom: 1px solid #CCCCCC

    tr:last-child
      border-bottom: none

    td
      font-size: 14px
      text-align: left
      vertical-align: middle
      white-space: nowrap
      text-overflow: ellipsis
      overflow-wrap: break
      padding: 8px 8px 8px 0


.input-search
  padding-bottom: 16px
  width: 250px

.cs-colum-sortble
  cursor: pointer
